flowPara.flowSpan: name: Find SAP XMLs by Shipment Number

flowRoot.flowPara: description: Enter shipment numbers to find corresponding SAP XML docs sqlAarrayFormat: shipment_numbers:

-- find sap documents (xml) by SAP shipment number SELECT document_id, feed_type, failed_message, process_state, source_path, state_changed AT TIME ZONE 'UTC' FROM sap_feed_documents WHERE feed_type = 'order_shipment' AND ( <% shipment_numbers %> ) ORDER BY state_changed DESC; schema: type: object required: - shipment_numbers properties: shipment_numbers: type: array title: A list of shipment numbers items: type: string
